{"word":"μαρτυρέω","slug":"μαρτυρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μαρτυρέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μάρτυς\">μάρτυς</a></el>] ‘attest to a fact or truth’, <b>testify, attest<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on confirmation and attestation, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b><a href='B:470 23:31'>Mt 23:31</a>; <a href='B:500 1:7'>J 1:7</a>, <a href='B:500 1:34'>34</a>; <a href='B:500 3:11'>3:11</a>; <a href='B:500 4:39'>4:39</a>; <a href='B:500 5:39'>5:39</a>; <a href='B:500 10:25'>10:25</a>; <a href='B:500 18:23'>18:23</a>;</b> <b><a href='B:500 21:24'>21:24</a>; <a href='B:510 15:8'>Ac 15:8</a>; <a href='B:510 22:5'>22:5</a>; <a href='B:510 23:11'>23:11</a>; <a href='B:520 10:2'>Ro 10:2</a>; <a href='B:530 15:15'>1 Cor 15:15</a>; <a href='B:550 4:15'>Gal 4:15</a>; <a href='B:580 4:13'>Col 4:13</a>; <a href='B:610 6:13'>1 Ti 6:13</a>; <a href='B:690 1:2'>1 J 1:2</a>; <a href='B:690 5:10'>5:10</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 3</a>; <a href='B:730 1:2'>Rv 1:2</a>; <a href='B:730 22:16'>22:16</a>, <a href='B:730 22:20'>20</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><a href='B:520 3:21'>Ro 3:21</a>; <a href='B:650 7:8'>Hb 7:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on rendering approval, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> <b><a href='B:490 4:22'>Lk 4:22</a>; <a href='B:510 16:2'>Ac 16:2</a>; <a href='B:650 11:4'>Hb 11:4b</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 12b</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><a href='B:510 6:3'>Ac 6:3</a>; <a href='B:510 10:22'>10:22</a>; <a href='B:510 22:12'>22:12</a>; <a href='B:650 11:4'>Hb 11:4a</a>, 39;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ impers.\">impers.</a> <b><a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 12a</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μάρμαρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"ri